## 9. DIGITAL FEATURES PLANNING

| Feature | Description | Safety / Ethical Considerations |
|---------|-------------|--------------------------------|
| **Anonymous Help Form** | One‑page, no‑login, encrypted message to counselors. | No IP logs; auto‑delete after 30 days. |
| **Awareness Blog** | Peer‑written articles, moderated pre‑publish. | Content review workflow; trigger warnings. |
| **Resource Library** | Searchable PDFs, videos, toolkits, multilingual. | PDF sanitisation, copyright check. |
| **Volunteer System** | Role‑based dashboards, hour‑tracking, badge system. | Background‑check opt‑in, data minimisation. |
| **Event Management** | Calendar of workshops, webinars; RSVP via email only. | No third‑party trackers; GDPR‑compliant. |
| **Reporting Resources** | Interactive map of nearest helplines, police contacts. | Verify up‑to‑date numbers; no auto‑share of location. |
| **Multilingual Support** | Hindi, English, regional languages (Tamil, Bengali, etc.) via i18n. | Professional translation, contextual accuracy. |
| **Helpline Integration** | Click‑to‑call/tap‑to‑chat phone numbers with “Do Not Record” flag. | Provide fallback email contact. |
| **Chatbot (optional)** | AI‑driven FAQ bot with strict content filters; escalation to human. | No storage of personal queries, content moderation. |
| **Cyber‑Safety Tools** | Browser‑extension checklist, downloadable “Safe‑Surf” guide. | Open‑source, no telemetry. |

