## 10. SOCIAL MEDIA & OUTREACH STRATEGY

| Channel | Tactics | Content Types | Frequency |
|---------|---------|---------------|-----------|
| **Instagram** | • Carousel posts with “Myth‑Busters”. <br>• Reels of 30‑sec youth stories. <br>• Highlight “Ask a Mentor” Q&A. | Visual infographics, short video clips, IG Stories polls. | 3–4 posts/week, daily Stories. |
| **YouTube (shorts)** | 15‑sec “Quick Tips” series (e.g., “how to pause a stressful moment”). | Video, subtitles in 3 languages. | 2 shorts/week. |
| **Twitter/X** | Threaded “Did you know?” facts; live‑tweet events. | Text + GIFs, retweet partner NGOs. | Daily. |
| **School Outreach** | Printable “Awareness Kit” for teachers; QR‑code to site. | Workshops, webinars, guest‑speaker sessions. | Quarterly visits per region. |
| **Campaigns** | “#SafeTalk” month – user‑generated stories (with consent). | Photo contests, gif‑maker tools. | 1‑month focused push per semester. |
| **Brand Safety** | No political hashtags; avoid sensational language; use consistent visual palette. |

